Statement of Purpose

The laws of most jurisdictions throughout the world automatically confer
exclusive Copyright and Related Rights upon the creator and subsequent
owner(s) of an original work of authorship and/or a database. The person
associating CC0 with a work ("Affirmer") dedicates the work to the public
domain by waiving all rights to the work worldwide under copyright law,
including all related and neighboring rights, to the extent allowed by law.

You can copy, modify, distribute and perform the work, even for commercial
purposes, all without asking permission.

No Copyright: To the extent possible under law, the author(s) have waived
all copyright and related or neighboring rights to this work.

